{"id":277351,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-维权人士、公民行动者、网友13亿公民（卫/","date":"2013-02-01T07:01:09Z","modified":"2013-02-01T07:01:09Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士、公民行动者、网友13亿公民（卫小兵）遭到陆丰警方讯问（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，著名的维权人士、公民行动者、网友</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民（真名：卫小兵）接到老婆电话，说有两名自称广东陆丰巿公安局的警察造访其公司，并对各类证件逐一登记。电话里对方不肯透露具体的部门，只说找</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民调查了解点事情，让</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民尽快回去到当地派出所接受询问调查。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民了解到的情况是，因为自己发起</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>在广州举行的网友公义饭醉活动，给良心犯募捐，和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011-2012</span><span>年三度到临沂探望陈光诚，并在临沂广场拉“光耀四海诚动未来”的横幅被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，现在分别面临诈骗和偷窃两项指控。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>随后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民</span><span>委托</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E6%A5%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%AD%E9%A3%9E%E9%9B%84\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">郭飞雄</span></span></a></span><span>帮自己提供法律援助以及安排辩护律师，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民表示，不怕进去，但绝不能背负如偷窃、诈骗之类的恶名进去。能够把一起众人皆知的声援陈光诚的事件定为偷窃，说明对方的无耻是没有底线的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民接到警方通知，让他在家里等候，马上来人面谈。对方声称，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民的事是上级交代下来的，与地方无关。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民随后被带到碣石清平派出所，接受陆丰公安的询问，并做了笔录，期间有网友打他电话他说不方便说话，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民回到家中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，在广州举行的网友公义饭醉活动中，现场总共募集到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10700</span><span>元现金，加上公义帐户上的余额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18474</span><span>，总共收到捐款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28174</span><span>元，经过在场网友的讨论，分别捐助给曹海波、陈西、张林、刘本琦等多位良心犯，具体见下图。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Jobu6kzQl9g/UQsrWFBf4PI/AAAAAAAAa68/-d3w6MoehQA/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"363\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Jobu6kzQl9g/UQsrWFBf4PI/AAAAAAAAa68/-d3w6MoehQA/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-keqge9f3kKs/UQsrXxf3nYI/AAAAAAAAa7E/g_ZGuTUE3WQ/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-keqge9f3kKs/UQsrXxf3nYI/AAAAAAAAa7E/g_ZGuTUE3WQ/s400/3.jpg\" width=\"298\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196,23630,14806]}